<para>Name &quot;redrawInScalingUp&quot;, type Property::BOOLEAN. <simplesect kind="note"><para>See also: <ref refid="classDali_1_1Ui_1_1LottieAnimationView_1a61ee7d70095361f73e82cfec5dc6a0be" kindref="member">LottieAnimationView::SetRedrawOnScaleUp()</ref>, <ref refid="classDali_1_1Ui_1_1LottieAnimationView_1a223899d128ecbbba3a70784b63ed3243" kindref="member">LottieAnimationView::IsRedrawOnScaleUp()</ref>. </para>
