          <briefdescription>
<para>The URL of the placeholder image shown while loading. </para>
          </briefdescription>
          <detaileddescription>
<para>Name &quot;placeholderImage&quot;, type Property::STRING. <simplesect kind="note"><para>See also: <ref refid="classDali_1_1Ui_1_1LottieAnimationView_1a7997b1952da8f5103d5852cc75cd8264" kindref="member">LottieAnimationView::SetPlaceholderUrl()</ref>, <ref refid="classDali_1_1Ui_1_1LottieAnimationView_1a66142b7e8d3d99cdf944044a465de206" kindref="member">LottieAnimationView::GetPlaceholderUrl()</ref>. </para>
</simplesect>
</para>
          </detaileddescription>
        </enumvalue>
